Version 0.99.14
===============================================================================
+ Bugfixes:
  - Filtering. Captures invalid user input.
  - Clustering. Parameter settings resulting in a minimum number of samples per
    initial state <= 1 are captured.

Version 0.99.13
===============================================================================
+ Bugfixes:
  - Visualization. Package is compatible with most recent ggplot2
    release (3.x.x).
+ Updated CITATION

